=== sw-cor24-rpg-ii Minimal RPG-II Demo (Second-Field Variant) ===
Program:
H  control header
F  input file INFIL
I  field 01: A0110  (10-char input slice)
I  field 02: A0810  (3-char input tail slice)
C  MOVE02 -> calc work field
O  DETAIL output (3 chars)

Current boundary:
- Real today: the external tiny source deck can now vary between two decoded
  I-spec fields, and the single MOVE-style C-spec selects which one feeds
  the output line.
- Placeholder today: there is still only one calc op, one output line, and
  one input file in the supported runtime-parsed subset.

Current runtime-produced output:
01A
02B
03C



